name: Sanji
description: Sanji is a meme token on Ethereum. Sanji is the mascot of ChatGPT and was shown to the world on the livestream launch of GPT-4o. Sanji is a community that wants to spread the joy of the dog and GPT-4o. The project aims to build a community and bring people together around Sanji. The goal of the community is to make Sanji one of the most recognized dogs in crypto and to support ChatGPT with Sanji the dog
